      "content": "it's just so hard to convince myself it's an emergency... i get really bad migraines all the time and they usually go away after a long sleep. like, if i just take a really high dose of tylenol and maybe some benadryl to help me sleep through the pain, wouldn't that just reset everything? if it was a stroke or something serious, wouldn't it be more obvious than just a weird face feeling and a headache?",
